Constants.html#/c:@SDLResultWrongLanguag.name: SDLResultWrongLanguage
Constants.html#/c:@SDLResultWrongLanguag.abstract: The requested language is currently not supported. Might be because of a mismatch of the currently active language on the head unit and the requested language.

Constants.html#/c:@SDLResultRejected.name: SDLResultRejected

Constants.html#/c:@SDLResultAborted.name: SDLResultAborted

Constants.html#/c:@SDLResultIgnored.abstract: A command was ignored, because the intended result is already in effect. For example, SetMediaClockTimer was used to pause the media clock although the clock is paused already.

Constants.html#/c:@SDLResultUnsupportedR.name: SDLResultUnsupportedResource

Constants.html#/c:@SDLResultFileNotFound.name: SDLResultFileNotFound

Constants.html#/c:@SDLResultTruncatedDat.name: SDLResultTruncatedData

Constants.html#/c:@SDLResultWarnings.name: SDLResultWarnings

Constants.html#/c:@SDLResultSaved.name: SDLResultSaved
